#KachCalls Episode 1 RECAP 
Last Monday our very first KACH calls episode we had a young lady call in to tell us about her love life. She’s an artist and she’s been crushing on the producer she’s been working with. They have had an attraction to each other for a few years now but they haven’t acted on it because she has a boyfriend and he has a girlfriend! For the full story check out the live pinned at the top of my page!
.
This call covered many relatable themes such as dating in the music industry vs. dating civilians, protecting yourself as a woman in music, working through relationships and choosing yourself over the BS. But I want to hear from you! If you are an artist, do you prefer to date someone who is in the industry or a civilian? Ladies, is dating in the industry worth it? If you’ve been in a long relationship and your love goes cold do you rekindle or leave? Lmk what you think below!
.
